turns.content: do you know what a juanola is?

Yes, "Juanola" is a brand name of a Spanish company that produces various types of candies, lozenges, and other confectionery products. The company is well known for its "Juanola Original" black licorice lozenges, which are popular in Spain and other Spanish-speaking countries. The company was founded in 1906 and has been producing sweets for over a century.
